data.description: SELLER WILL PAY $5,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COST w/ acceptable offer. Welcome to 8129 Resplandor in beautiful Corpus Christi! This charming abode presents a perfect blend of comfort and style, offering a spacious family room that seamlessly flows into a well-appointed kitchen. Enjoy the luxury of ample counter space, all adorned with exquisite granite countertops and a tasteful full tumbled marble backsplash. Cooking and entertaining become a delight in this culinary haven. Step outside and discover your own oasis – an extended patio that invites relaxation and outdoor gatherings. The oversized yard provides endless possibilities, from gardening to playtime, making it a true haven for both adults and children alike. Experience the ultimate in convenience and aesthetic appeal in this lovely Corpus Christi residence. Don't miss the chance to call 8129 Resplandor your new home.
